Cell["\<\

Take contractions over (1,2) to be positive, it follows that contraction over \
(1,3) is negative. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9804077285952864`*^9, 3.980407767015341*^9}, {
  3.9804713545105357`*^9, 3.98047135468668*^9}, {3.980490560479523*^9, 
